OL,3,CManchester Arena survivors awarded
OL,4,C#45,000 in damages after harassment
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FTwo survivors of the Manchester Arena
OL,8,Fbombing have been awarded a total of
OL,9,F#45,000 in damages in the High Court
OL,10,Fafter suing a man who claims the
OL,11,Fattack was staged.
OL,13,FMartin Hibbert and his daughter Eve
OL,14,Fsued Richard Hall for harassment and
OL,15,Fdata protection over his claims in
OL,16,Fseveral videos and a book that the
OL,17,Fattack was staged.
OL,19,FMr Hall, former TV producer, also
OL,20,Fclaimed that they were involved as
OL,21,F"crisis actors".
