OL,3,CManchester Arena survivors awarded
OL,4,C#45,000 in damages after harassment
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FThe pair suffered life-changing
OL,8,Finjuries at the Ariana Grande concert
OL,9,Fin May 2017, with Mr Hibbert left with
OL,10,Fa spinal cord injury and Miss Hibbert
OL,11,Ffacing severe brain damage.
OL,13,FMr Hall claimed his actions `
OL,14,Fincluding filming Miss Hibbert outside
OL,15,Fher home ` were in the public interest
OL,16,Fas a journalist, and that "millions of
OL,17,Fpeople have bought a lie" about the
OL,18,Fattack.
