OL,3,CManchester Arena survivors awarded
OL,4,C#45,000 in damages after harassment
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FSpeaking outside the court Mr Hibbert
OL,8,Fsaid: "The judge has found that Mr
OL,9,FHall's actions surmounted to
OL,10,Fharassment, that they had caused added
OL,11,Falarm, distress and anxiety to both me
OL,12,Fand my daughter. It was oppressive and
OL,14,Funacceptable.
OL,16,F"Freedom of expression provides
OL,17,Fprotection for journalism, but Mr Hall
OL,18,Fhas abused media freedom.
