OL,3,CManchester Arena survivors awarded
OL,4,C#45,000 in damages after harassment
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,F"He repeatedly published false
OL,8,Fallegations and dismissed the tragic
OL,9,Freality which so many ordinary people
OL,10,Fhave experienced and continue to live
OL,11,Fwith.
OL,13,F"His abhorrent behaviour had to be
OL,14,Fchallenged, not just for me and my
OL,15,Ffamily but for others too.
OL,17,F"I am pleased with the judgment, and
OL,18,Fthe comments of the Judge as to how
OL,19,Funacceptable Hall's behaviour was. It
OL,20,Fis a comprehensive victory for us.
