OL,3,CManchester Arena survivors awarded
OL,4,C#45,000 in damages after harassment
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,F"I want this to case to open the door
OL,8,Ffor change, and for it to protect
OL,9,Fothers from what we have been put
OL,10,Fthrough.
OL,12,F"The case has highlighted and proved
OL,13,Fthat there is protection within the
OL,14,Flaw, and it sends out a message to
OL,15,Fconspiracy theorists that you cannot
OL,16,Fignore all acceptable evidence and
OL,17,Fharass innocent people."
