OL,3,CManchester Arena survivors awarded
OL,4,C#45,000 in damages after harassment
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FIn a judgment in October, Mrs Justice
OL,8,FSteyn ruled in favour of the Hibberts
OL,9,Fand described Mr Hall's behaviour as
OL,10,F"a negligent, indeed reckless, abuse
OL,11,Fof media freedom".
OL,13,FAt a hearing on Friday 8 November, the
OL,14,Fjudge said Mr Hibbert and his daughter
OL,15,Fwould each be awarded #22,500 in
OL,16,Fdamages. Mr Hall was also told to pay
OL,17,F90% of the Hibberts' legal costs.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@QO]
