OL,3,CManchester Arena survivors awarded
OL,4,C#45,000 in damages after harassment
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FThe final figure may be determined by
OL,8,Fa specialist judge if an agreement is
OL,9,Fnot reached, but the court heard their
OL,10,Ftotal is currently estimated at
OL,11,F#260,000.
OL,13,FJonathan Price, for the pair, said Mr
OL,14,FHall's behaviour was "towards the more
OL,15,Foppressive end of the spectrum of
OL,16,Fharassing conduct".
