OL,3,CManchester Arena survivors awarded
OL,4,C#45,000 in damages after harassment
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FHe continued in written submissions:
OL,8,F"In a series of widely viewed videos,
OL,9,Fa print publication, as well as during
OL,10,Fin-person lectures, the defendant
OL,11,Finsisted that the terrorist attack in
OL,12,Fwhich the claimants were
OL,13,Fcatastrophically injured did not
OL,14,Fhappen and that the claimants were
OL,15,Fparticipants or 'crisis actors' in a
OL,16,Fstate-orchestrated hoax, who had
OL,17,Frepeatedly, publicly and egregiously
OL,18,Flied to the public for monetary gain."
