OL,3,CManchester Arena survivors awarded
OL,4,C#45,000 in damages after harassment
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FMr Price had said a total of #75,000
OL,8,Ffor the pair in damages should be
OL,9,Fawarded, as well as at least 90% of
OL,10,Ftheir legal fees.
OL,12,FPaul Oakley, for Mr Hall, said in
OL,13,Fwritten submissions that #7,500 each
OL,14,Fin damages "would be appropriate",
OL,15,Fadding there was "no justification"
OL,16,Ffor aggravated damages.
OL,18,FHe told the court: "There is no
OL,19,Fallegation of malice and that is
OL,20,Freally a fundamental point as far as
OL,21,Fdamages are concerned."
