OL,3,CManchester Arena survivors awarded
OL,4,C#45,000 in damages after harassment
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,F"Some of these harassment cases can
OL,8,Fget pretty nasty, but there was no
OL,9,Fvindictiveness."
OL,11,FMr Oakley later said that a suggested
OL,12,Finjunction was too wide, describing it
OL,13,Fas "a blanket ban" on all of Mr Hall's
OL,14,Foutput, and called the Hibberts'
OL,15,Festimated costs as "jaw dropping".
OL,17,FThe barrister said: "Mr Hall's work
OL,18,Fwas 'not about' the claimants, who
OL,19,Ffeatured only minimally in the
OL,20,Fentirety of his recorded and written
OL,21,Foutput.
